{"tid":2260040,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[正經系列]發明咗個復仇者蚊拍","createTime":"2020-10-27T09:28:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T05:08:38.000Z","uid":51346,"like":41,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"19978829952216e5ecb1860cac3acbc98f79ffca","tid":2260040,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T09:28:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O4CSqhT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO4CSqhT.gif&h=657c1f2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n拍唔中隻衰蚊 好嬲嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wfG4gpG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwfG4gpG.jpg&h=4882d917&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解叫復仇者係因為你要先俾隻蚊吸血 至發動到呢塊蚊拍嘅效果 <br />\n<br />\n中間圓形係磁鐵 可以對隻吸完血嘅蚊有影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Ja8H5G.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Ja8H5G.gif&h=55f3faea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n血液有抗磁性 所以咁大杯血都推得郁 一拎個拍出嚟 啲蚊咁細會直接撞埋牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v3dBRZv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv3dBRZv.gif&h=01a0be51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n磁鐵對住隻蚊個方位 基本上之後係任你魚肉<br />\n<br />\n而且我懷疑未行到埋去電佢 啲磁力已經逼爆隻蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\npost尾彩蛋<br />\n蚊拍殺人大法<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KLLsYFq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKLLsYFq.gif&h=cf00595e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n血抗磁性細啲：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zzfD5kC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzzfD5kC.gif&h=d29f7662&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一樣就可以定喺空中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n血抗磁性大啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cx0XBsu.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCx0XBsu.gif&h=80c6f54f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1cddd955c70306eb0c089703f8ea6f5c26b0614","tid":2260040,"uid":51346,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T09:28:29.000Z","msg":"有緣再會"},{"pid":"271bbda074f4f50fd20cc538db961a185b41f424","tid":2260040,"uid":374184,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T09:28:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3f4c64d92be4aff056124ba64e964ab6f2085010","tid":2260040,"uid":201299,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T09:28:47.000Z","msg":"gif?"},{"pid":"65955bc43c819c353a077ff671f6aec18fcc60eb","tid":2260040,"uid":110113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T09:28:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bda90bb6bf297e2821354cb6d745f3d3443279ae","tid":2260040,"uid":374184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T09:28:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eafcb9194106b88d5e5ecc8b1017d5a6c475cbdc","tid":2260040,"uid":226251,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T09:28:55.000Z","msg":"今次啲圖ok <br />\n10/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c683279c6069aa6235cace317268c113454ebd94","tid":2260040,"uid":350634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T09:29:37.000Z","msg":"殺狗得唔得"},{"pid":"4c09854b02b3880e6f4f183a3879607831fc3339","tid":2260040,"uid":164239,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T09:32:00.000Z","msg":"最尾, 廬根 vs 磁力王<